==古生物學==
[[File:Heyuannia_and_eggs_nest.jpg|thumb]]
[[File:Ajancingenia_reconstruction.png|thumb]]
在屬於河源龍的蛋殼中發現了[[膽綠素|膽綠素]]和{{link-en|原紫質IX|Protoporphyrin IX}}，顯示牠們的蛋殼是藍綠色的。這種顏色能夠同時提供偽裝及性信號，亦可見於現代[[旅鶇|旅鶇]]和{{link-en|平胸鳥類|Ratite}}。蛋殼排列顯示河源龍的巢穴部分開放，可能代表著有多位親屬參與照顧。<ref name=wiemannetal2017>{{cite journal | last1 = Wiemann | first1 = J. | last2 = Yang | first2 = T.-R. | last3 = Sander | first3 = P.N. | last4 = Schneider | first4 = M. | last5 = Engeser | first5 = M. | last6 = Kath-Schorr | first6 = S. | last7 = Müller | first7 = C.E. | last8 = Sander | first8 = P.M. | year = 2017 | title = Dinosaur origin of egg color: oviraptors laid blue-green eggs | doi = 10.7717/peerj.3706 | journal = PeerJ | volume = 5 | page = e3706 | url = https://peerj.com/articles/3706/ | pmc = 5580385 | pmid = 28875070 | access-date = 2021-08-02 | archive-date = 2022-01-03 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220103150719/https://peerj.com/articles/3706/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>

